data.description: This house offers an open concept with kitchen , dining area, family room, under-stairs play area & 1/2 bath just off of the family room. Separate living room in the front with hidden TV cable setup. Roomy master suite: walk-in closet w/wood shelving, bath w/dual sinks, jetted tub, and standing shower. Laundry room with utility sink upstairs near bedrooms. Two-car garage with automatic door opener, heating & A/C unit and exterior backyard door. There is also extra storage space in the garage attic. Fully fenced yard w/timed UGS, natural gas valve ready for the BBQ and this backyard is ready for relaxation and play. Close to park, new STEM school, and shopping. Watch the GESA Stadium Fireworks from your own yard!
data.whatILove:
-Has a perfect view of the dust devils fireworks
-Great new STEM elementary school near by
-Great park near by
-GREAT Neighbors
